_sText:
This map was a request at first I didn’t want to redo it because it was made by my friend Omi but I never got in contact with him and I already had the original files so I decided to give it a go

This is a short list of fixes I Have for the map there will be more to come soon when I put out the next version

-Crashes
-Vents
-Lighting Turning off for no reason
-Glitches in the physics 
-Gameplay 

More things to come in the next beta and a possible expansion 

I take no credit for this map in anyway just the fixes Also Omi wont care if I remake his map because we are cool and he made it for zombie mod league and I’m currently working on the project for sometime in late august for during the winter. 

(I will take this down if the mapper asks me to)
